        <p><span facs="#zone_f9c17888-c397-11e8-8fd8-f40f243b5e05">東京帝國大學總長海軍技術中將從三位勳一等</span><span facs="#zone_f9c179f8-c397-11e8-907c-f40f243b5e05">工學博士男爵平賀讓病氣中</span><span facs="#zone_f9c17aca-c397-11e8-a81a-f40f243b5e05">,</span><span facs="#zone_f9c17b68-c397-11e8-a5ce-f40f243b5e05">處二月十七日莞</span><span facs="#zone_f9c17c14-c397-11e8-8d6a-f40f243b5e05">去致候間此段御通知中上候</span><span facs="#zone_f9c17cb4-c397-11e8-8997-f40f243b5e05">追了東京帝國大學葬7以了佛式二依</span><span facs="#zone_f9c17d4a-c397-11e8-be95-f40f243b5e05">,</span><span facs="#zone_f9c17dd8-c397-11e8-8618-f40f243b5e05">東京帝國大學大講堂</span><span facs="#zone_f9c17e76-c397-11e8-8598-f40f243b5e05">二於了來儿二十三日午後一時三十分my葬儀三時my四時</span><span facs="#zone_f9c17f0c-c397-11e8-9515-f40f243b5e05">マテ告別式相営可申候</span><span facs="#zone_f9c17fa2-c397-11e8-8118-f40f243b5e05">尚御供物等八時節柄堅夕御辞退申上候</span><span facs="#zone_f9c18038-c397-11e8-963b-f40f243b5e05">昭和十八年二月十七日</span><span facs="#zone_f9c180d0-c397-11e8-a7f2-f40f243b5e05">東京市世田谷代田二丁目10五七番地</span><span facs="#zone_f9c18164-c397-11e8-b5fe-f40f243b5e05">男</span><span facs="#zone_f9c181ee-c397-11e8-b065-f40f243b5e05">平賀</span><span facs="#zone_f9c18292-c397-11e8-8e73-f40f243b5e05">謙</span><span facs="#zone_f9c18324-c397-11e8-9af4-f40f243b5e05">東京帝國大學</span></p></body>
